name: GIXXER 155CC (SD)
description: Here is the latest version of your favorite street sport bike with the same engine specifications and engine test as the Gixxer. With its new advanced Disc-Brake, it promises a really fabulous, more stable and more confident riding experience on all kinds of terrain. Another addition Gixxer Monotone Classic Plus comes with two variants; Brilliant Silver & Majestic Yellow. Another edition to Gixxer Monotone Series, Gixxer Classic Matt comes in 3 new colors; Matt Cobalt Blue, Matt Elegant Black, and Matt Majestic Red. Gixxer Monotone Classic Plus & Gixxer Classic Matt both series

name: GIXXER 155CC Fi-Disc
description: The New Gixxer is featured with the muscular street bike styling right, the overall ethos of the appearance is premium & stylish. There’s a large, sculpted fuel tank that takes center stage, and the flat, wide handlebars give the New Gixxer a butch stance. The New Gixxer’s sharp look is also thanks to the LED headlight and tail-lamp that Suzuki is offering. Turn indicators continue to be conventional bulbs. Instrumentation is a fully digital affair with read-outs like two trip meters and real-time fuel efficiency being shown. Single-channel ABS ensures safety when panic braking.
